title: Lunchbox & Eddie Battle It Out In Plank Off + Eric Church Talks About Getting Kicked Off A Tour Early In His Career
itunes:title: Lunchbox & Eddie Battle It Out In Plank Off + Eric Church Talks About Getting Kicked Off A Tour Early In His Career
description:
Lunchbox and Eddie compete in a ‘plank off’ challenge for Bobby’s money. Eric Church talks to Bobby about getting kicked off a tour and replaced with Taylor Swift before she was a superstar. Also, Bobby talks about a Memorial Day pool party he had at his house.
